description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 56, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 168, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60563-11410-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [168 Votes, Top 10% Score]
